node.text:
Teaching students how to be an advocate and ally 🏳️‍🌈 can be engaging and creative with this activity! #ad I teamed up with @michaelsstores to help you teach your student about the importance of advocacy.

Be sure to grab all of your favorite multi-colored and alphabet beads for kids at your local Michaels stores for this project with your students! #makeitwithmichaels

#michaelspartner #teachersofig #teachersofinstagram #iteachtoo #teachersofinsta #teachingadvocacy

node.text:
GIVEAWAY 🎉: Attention k-5 public school teachers, @nuggetcomfort is giving away a series of Nuggets every 4-6 weeks!!! 🤯 All you have to do is fill out the form using the link in my bio and you’ll be entered!

I love using @nuggetcomfort in my makeovers because they’re flexible, comfortable and washable! It’s a win-win every way you look at it.

You can nominate yourself and/or another K-5 public school teacher! What are you waiting for!? Tap that link in my bio and potentially win a Nugget!

https://nuggetcomfort.com/pages/nugget-teacher-donation-program

#nuggetcomfort #flexibleseating #activeseating #iteachtoo #teachersofig #teachersofinstagram #teachersofinsta #teachersfollowteachers #teacherssupportteachers

node.text:
✈️🌎 Turn your students into world travelers with this informational text resource! With 20+ nonfiction articles ✏️ and corresponding activities/projects, 📓 your students will learn to dissect and annotate while simultaneously learning about different cultures and countries.

I designed this resource to help students strengthen their reading, writing, and analyzing skills. The journal is designed with 20 unique informational text articles (from 20 countries around the world)! Each article is paired with comprehension questions and a variety of activities and projects.

Link to resource in bio: https://www.teacherspayteachers.com/Product/Travel-Journal-20-Informational-Text-Articles-Activities-Grades-4-7-DIGITAL-4706090

#englishteacher #iteachela #iteachenglish #upperelementary #iteach456 #iteach678 #iteachmiddleschool #informationaltext #iteach5th #iteach6th #middleschoolteacher

node.text:
Do you teach upper elementary, middle school or high school? If so, I have hundreds of teacher approved ✅ activities, projects and bundles to help you prep for back-to-school!

For years, I’ve designed hands-on, engaging resources for you to use with your students. I spend a lot of time on each piece making sure it’s something that it’s appealing AND functional!

In fact, more than 50,000 teachers have given 5-star ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ reviews on my resources.

Today is the last day of the site-wide sale, so be sure to grab anything you need to save!

Link in bio: https://www.teacherspayteachers.com/Store/The-Superhero-Teacher

Ps: this is my Figurative Language Interactive Notebook

💪🏼🛠 It’s MaKeOvEr time!!! Picked up the Uhaul today and went all around Columbus picking up furniture. Excited to transform another space with my team!

Also, lots of new followers lately. Welcome to my little corner of the internet! This is my wife— she’s 8 months pregnant and a total rockstar. I share a lot about her and if that’s not something you can support, feel free to unfollow!

For the rest of you incredible humans who have so openly rooted for us along the way, we appreciate you! Pumped to share another makeover with you!

📓✏️ Exit tickets were my go-to for classroom management, routine and reflection when I was in the classroom, so I designed an exit ticket journal with daily exit ticket prompts!

Click the link in my bio to see if this resource works for you and your students!

Details:
- Printer friendly
- Digital included
- Any subject area
- Focuses on reflection + student understanding
- Daily prompts for the entire year
- No prep for you
